<plot>There's something special about Paul's day. With a bounce in his step and a twinkle in his eye, it seems nothing can bring him down. The story is one that anyone can understand, but not a single word is used in the telling of it. A smart, albeit strange piece, about the meanings and interpretations gleaned from the simplest of body languages.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?399637</url></doc>
